drinking game
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a game or contest for drinkers involving some feat, the non-peformance of which involves finishing the drink in hand and starting the feat again.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
